net.floodlightcontroller.flowcache
Class QRFlowCacheObj

java.lang.Object
  net.floodlightcontroller.flowcache.QRFlowCacheObj

public class QRFlowCacheObj
extends java.lang.Object

Used in BigFlowCacheQueryResp as query result. Used to return one flow when queried by one of the big flow cache APIs. One of these QRFlowCacheObj is returned for each combination of priority and action.
